# AppBar Grey Strip Issue on Lower Android Devices

## Problem
On lower Android devices (API < 30), an **extra grey strip with app label** appears above the AppBar.

## Cause
`AndroidManifest.xml` had no theme or wrong theme, so Android used **default label**.

## Solution
Update `AndroidManifest.xml`:

```xml
<application
    android:label=""
    android:theme="@style/Theme.MaterialComponents.DayNight.NoActionBar"
    android:usesCleartextTraffic="true">
